c: 39
v: 38
t: "If you ask them, \"Who has created the heavens and the earth?\" They will certainly say, \"God has created them.\" Ask them, \"Do you think that you can rescue me from the punishment of God with which He may afflict me? Can you prevent His mercy if He wants to grant it to me?\" Say, \"God is Sufficient (support) for me. In Him alone one must trust"